verbose_text: Expression of VDR protein in PTC was notably higher (51 out of 78, 65.4%) than that observed in paired adjacent non cancerous tissue (21 out of 78, 26.9%), and IHC staining was localized in cytoplasm of PTC (XREF_FIG), whereas IHC staining was localized in nuclei of paired adjacent non cancerous tissue (XREF_FIG).
